# INShareFocusStatusIntentResponseCode.success

**Case**

Your intent handler successfully updated the user’s communication status.

## Declaration

```swift
case success
```

## Handling the Intent

- **INShareFocusStatusIntentResponseCode.inProgress**: Your intent handler is handling the intent, but it may take some time.
